        "PasswordHash": "AQAAAAIAAYagAAAAEN9jQFR6FQCOZbYizpTogkRJBwF86TAmCFBuf7yn8smwVeH0GKwBRifSIc1G7Kd0wQ==",
        "Role": "ItManager"
      }
